    + deletion of symlinks created by some buggy configurations.
      (Closes: #550152)
    + some issues related to CD/DVD burners. (Closes: #573402, #577256)
    + Logitech keyboards broken by the broken fix for #567237.
      (Closes: #575548, #576441)
